  "text": "• Burns: Studies of patients recovering from significant burns show that abnormal sensations such as paresthesia are frequently reported as long as several years after the injury [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Furthermore long-term paresthesia is a complication reported after electrical burns [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
